        "text": "The lONIQ 5 is proven worldwide for its prowess in electrification and sustainability. With its global award-winning DNA, Hyundai now begins a pivotal journey with the IONIQ 5 robotaxi, a level 4 autonomous vehicle that can drive without a driver. More than 30 sensors including LiDAR, and a computing system allows the robotaxi to detect 360° and make optimal decisions. Hyundai is beginning production of the IONIQ 5 robotaxi, which is set to launch in Las Vegas during the first half of 2024.",
